
## BUG-UI-001
**Bug Name:** Button Alignment Issue  
**Severity:** Low  
**Priority:** Medium  
**Frequency:** 100%

**Description:**  
The "Submit" button on the contact form is not properly aligned with other form elements on mobile devices.

**Steps to Reproduce:**
1. Open the contact page on a mobile device
2. Observe the "Submit" button position

**Expected Result:** Button should be centered and aligned with form fields

**Actual Result:** Button appears offset to the right

**Environment:** iOS Safari, Chrome Mobile  
**Screenshot:** [Attached]

