## BUG-UI-002
**Bug Name:** Inconsistent Font Sizes  
**Severity:** Low  
**Priority:** Low  
**Frequency:** 100%

**Description:**  
Header fonts have inconsistent sizes across different pages.

**Steps to Reproduce:**
1. Navigate to the Home page and note the header size
2. Navigate to the About page
3. Compare header sizes

**Expected Result:** All page headers should have consistent font sizes

**Actual Result:** Header sizes vary between 24px and 28px

**Environment:** All browsers  
**Screenshot:** [Attached]

